snippet.title: 31-year-old Ratan Tata’s closest aide Shantanu escorts his mortal remains ahead of State funeral
snippet.description:
Ratan Tata, the 86-year-old chairman emeritus of Tata Sons, one of India's largest and most prominent companies, died on October 9. Due to his age, the business tycoon was brought to Mumbai's Breach Candy Hospital for a standard checkup. However, his situation deteriorated during the past week. Business tycoons, took to X to pay tribute to Ratan Tata for his exemplary work in India’s Industrial growth. 

#RatanTata #TataGroup #Tata #RatanTataNews #shantanunaidu

#RatanTata  #ShantanuNaidu  #Tata

snippet.title: #Video | Chumma Chumma | चुम्मा चुम्मा | Khesari Lal Yadav | Shilpi Raj | Rajaram | नया भोजपुरी गाना
snippet.description:
देखि Chumma Anthem Of The Year अउरी तैयार हो जाई रवुआ सब झूमे खातिर ट्रेंडिंग स्टार खेसारी लाल यादव और आकांशा पूरी के साथ "चुम्मा चुम्मा " पे।'

Subscribe to our channel for more Bhojpuri Songs:
https://youtube.com/c/SaregamaHumBhojpuri

Credits:-

Title :- Chumma Chumma
Singer :- Khesari Lal Yadav & Shilpi Raj
Feat :- Akanksha Puri
Film Name:- Rajaram
Film Director:- Parag Patil
Song Director :- Sooraj Katoch (Zenith)
Lyrics :- Pinku Baba
Music :- Vinay Vinayak 
Choreographer :- Geeta Tamta (Zenith)
Dop- Rahul Yadav 
Editor :- Anand Kumar (Santu)
Associate Dop - Priyanshu Vats 
Focus Puller- Chandan Singh
Dance troupe :- Zenith
Dance Group :- (PK) Kamlesh 
GFX :- Suraj Vishwakarma 
DI :- Rohit Singh 
Production :- Amit Singh
All Costume:- Reema (Zai fashion )
Makeup Hair:- Vikash Kumar and Aryan Rajesh

Film Credits:

Production:- Technician Film Factory 
Producers :- Parag Patil & R.R. Prince

Lyrics:-

F-  फ्लेक्सी कमरिया पे नजरें गड़ाते हो 
     क्या बात है जो ये डॉलर उड़ाते हो 
M- लाली देखाके ललचावत बाड़ू 
      सुतल फीलिंग के जगावत बाड़ू 
      त दे द ना एगो नमूना 
      चूमा चूमा दे द, चूमा चूमा दे द चूमा 
F- चूमा चूमा ना देम, चूमा चूमा ना देम चूमा 

                     अंतरा -1
F-  अरे इंस्टा की मै तो रानी हूँ 
      तेरे जैसे हैँ फैन लाखों में 
      क्यूँ दूँ मै तुझे चुम्मा 
      सपना देखो बस रातों में 
M- द मौका, ल मौका -2
      गारंटी बा मजा आई हो 
      नाही देबू त दुख होइ दूना 
      चूमा चूमा दे.........

     
                   अंतरा -2
F-  मेरा चुम्मा तो बड़ी महँगा है
     बोलो क्या दोगे मुझे चुम्मे का 
     अरे मेकप में बड़े खर्चे हैँ 
     रेट लाखों हैँ मुझे छूने का 
M-  द खरचा, के परचा -2
      सब डॉलर में दे दियाई हो 
      बा रइसी रानी बुझ तु उ ना 
      चूमा चूमा दे...

snippet.title: Ratan Tata को खोकर Simi Garewal हुई भावुक, ऐसी है दोनों की अनोखी Love Story!
snippet.description:
द लेडी इन व्हाइट.. सिमी ग्रेवाल मशहूर एक्ट्रेस रही हैं. एक्टिंग से दूर होने के बाद इसलिए मशहूर हुई क्योंकि उनके शो में बड़ी बड़ी फिल्मी हस्तियां, सेलिब्रिटीज आते रहे. सिमी ऐसे सवाल पूछती हैं जिससे कोई भी निजी जिंदगी के राज खोल दे. शो का नाम रोंदेवू विद सिमी ग्रेवाल...सिमी ग्रेवाल चर्चा में हैं क्योंकि एक जमाने के बहुत करीबी रतन टाटा नहीं रहे. हमेशा स्माइल करने वाली सिमी ग्रेवाल अब टूट गई हैं. रतन के जाने का गम बर्दाश्त करने के लिए बेहद भारी है. रतन टाटा के चले जाने पर सिमी ग्रेवाल ने अपने एक्स अकाउंट पर अपने शो रोंदेवू विद सिमी ग्रेवाल की 2012 में ली गई अपनी और रतन टाटा की फोटो शेयर करते हुए विदाई दी और बस इतना ही लिखा - वे कहते हैं कि तुम चले गए... तुम्हारा जाना बहुत बड़ा नुकसान और इसे सहना बहुत मुश्किल है...अलविदा मेरे दोस्त...रतन टाटा...

#simigarewal #simigarewalbiography #ratantatalovestory #ratantata #tatagroup #simigarewallovestory

snippet.title: Harvesting Taro to make Payasam | Seppankizhangu Payasam Vlog in Tamil
snippet.description:
In this video join me as we harvest some Taro from our garden and make some recipes with it. The taro plant is very easy to grow. Just bury some small tuber bulbs in the garden and they grow and produce a lot of small tubers. Normally taro / seppankilangu can be made into a poriyal and slow roasted on a pan to make it crispy but in this vlog, we will try to make a seppankizhangu payasam and at the end the payasam tasted more like a paal kozhukattai recipe.
#tarovlog #seppankizhangu 

Friends, hope you liked this week's vlog and hope you will also try to grow some plants at home. See you soon with more interesting vlogs.

snippet.title: हलवा पूरी और चना अष्टमी नवमी प्रसाद के लिए | Ashtami Navami Prasad Recipe  |Halwa Poori Chana Recipe
snippet.description:
#ashtamiprasadrecipe #kalachanamasala #recipe #kabitaskitchen 

Ingredients:
For Poori:
Wheat flour - 1.5 cups
Water
Cooking oil to fry

For Halwa:
Sooji -1/2 cup
Sugar - 1/2 cup
Water - 1.5 cups
Saffron - 2 pinch
Ghee -  1/4 cup
Raisins - 1 tbsp
Alomonds -1 tbsp

Chane ki sabzi
Bengal gram (chana ) - 2 cups ( soaked)
Bay leaves - 2
Black cardamom - 2
Heat 2 tbsp of ghee
Cumin seeds - 1 tsp
Ginger - 2 tbsp
Green chilli - 4
Turmeric powder - 1/2 tsp
Chilli powder - 1 tsp
Coriander powder- 1 tbsp
Cumin powder - 1/2 tsp
Ghee - 2 tbsp
Peanut oil - 2 tbsp
Sendha Namak

snippet.title: Kaffara Episode 82 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 10th October 2024
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kaffara Episode 82 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 10th October 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

snippet.title: रतन टाटा
snippet.description: रतन टाटा के निधन से इस बात को लेकर बहस होनी चाहिए कि क्या भारत में नियमों और नैतिकता पर चलते हुए बिज़नेस साम्राज्य खड़ा किया जा सकता है? आज भले बात करने का दिन न हो लेकिन इस पर बात होनी चाहिए। रतन टाटा अपने जीवन में कई कंपनियां खड़ी कीं, लेकिन लोग उन कंपनियों के नाम से आगे जाकर इस शख़्स को याद कर रहे हैं। उन्हें लेकर भावुक हैं। क्या ये सभी रतन टाटा को उन उद्योगपतियों से अलग देखते हैं जिनकी चर्चा रतन टाटा से ज़्यादा होती है।

snippet.title: ആൻഡമാൻ ഗ്രാമത്തിൽ കല്യാണം കഴിക്കുന്നവർ സൂക്ഷിക്കണം! Attending a wedding uninvited in Andaman
snippet.description:
ഏത് നാട്ടിൽ ചെന്നാലും ഒരു കല്യാണം കൂടാൻ പരമാവധി നമ്മൾ ശ്രമിക്കാറുണ്ട്. അങ്ങനെയാണ് ക്ഷണിച്ചില്ലെങ്കിലും ആൻഡമാനിലെ ഈ കല്യാണത്തിന് ഞങ്ങൾ പോയത്😊
Attending a wedding uninvited in Andaman.
Exploring India’s biggest archipelago - Andaman and Nicobar islands
----------------

ആൻഡമാനിൽനിന്ന് കേസിൽപ്പെട്ട വിവരങ്ങൾ പങ്കുവെക്കുന്ന വീഡിയോ: https://youtu.be/igXTSKqvhHI?si=sI4vmCLApEgMhQGm

Kaffara Episode 81 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 9th October 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

snippet.title: क्या Iyer और Jetha खा पाएँगे इतना बड़ा Sada Dosa? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony SAB Channel:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

The men from the Gokuldham society are shocked that the ladies did not pick up the call. The ladies file a complaint at the police station about the bike. The society members are tensed that the ladies did not receive a call even after consistently trying it. Bhide and the society members are shocked after learning that Madhavi has filed a complaint about a bike stolen from the market before. Inspector Chalu Pande assures Bhide that the search team is consistently tracing the location of his bike and will find it soon. 

Show Name: Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast: Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt 
Produced By: Asit Kumar Modi 

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #sab #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble for all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son, he calls his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal. 

Click here to watch more episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7a-p97oXBuuoyLMAq7Ktx_h
 
क्या Iyer और Jetha खा पाएँगे इतना बड़ा Sada Dosa? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

Jethalal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble for all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son, he calls his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.description:
#vettaiyan #thalaivar170 #vettaiyanreview

 
Watch the Thalaivar’s 170th film Vettaiyan early and first review in Telugu by Cinemapicha.
 
Vettaiyan is an Indian Tamil language action drama film directed by T. J. Gnanavel and produced by Subaskaran's Lyca Productions. Starting Thalaivar Rajinikanth, Amitabh Bachchan, Manju Warrier, Dushara Vijayan, Fahadh Faasil, and Ritika Singh. The Worldwide release on 10th October 2024. This vettaiyan film was dubbed into many languages including Telugu, Hindi.
 
For more details about this film, watch the complete review of the film given by Cinemapicha. Do not skip the video and watch until the end.

snippet.title: Kaffara Episode 80 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 8th October 2024
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kaffara Episode 80 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 8th October 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi 
Director: Muhammad Iftikhar Iffi
Writer: Shafia Khan

Hey Guys, 
Welcome to my Youtube Channel,
I'm Jonathan Amaral, you might know me as Jonathan Gaming.
I started my professional Esports Career competing in Pubg Mobile Championships (Now BGMI),
Since the start of my career, I have been consistent with my gameplay and always been working hard to achieve my goals via winning Domestic/Global Championships. 
"The only player you should try to be better than is the player you were yesterday."

snippet.title: કળીયુગ ના ફેલ દિકરા//Gujarati Comedy Video//કોમેડી વિડીયો SB HINDUSTANI
snippet.description:
…..All of our videos are made for entertainment.
Every video has nothing to do with reality.....


****અમારા વિડીયોમા અમે કોઇપણ જાતી-ધર્મ નો વિરોધ કરતા નથી*****

અમારા દરેક વિડીયો ફેમીલી સાથે જોઈ સકાય છે

અમારી ચેનલના વીડીયો તમને ગમતા હોય તો અમારી ચેનલને સબસ્ક્રાઇબ કરવા નમ્ર વિનંતી 🙏

Director:-Balwantsinh Vamaiya

Office management:-Bharatsinh Vamaiya

Story by:-Vaghubha &Zalubha 

Editor :-Balwantsinh Vamaiya//Vaghubha Vamaiya//Abhik//DK

snippet.title: Mohammad Faiz - Tu Hi Tu | Jitendra Kumar | Zahrah S Khan | Arvvindr S Khaira | Bunny | Sagar
snippet.description:
Desi Melodies presents "Tu Hi Tu," a beautiful romantic track sung by the prodigy Mohammad Faiz. This one’s all about that dreamy, heart-touching vibe where Bunny has created a tune that’ll stay in your head, and Sagar’s lyrics hit right in the feels. Starring Jitendra Kumar and Zahra S Khan, the short film directed by Arvvindr S Khaira is all about their sweet love story, capturing the kind of love that makes you forget everything else.

Listen to ‘Tu Hi Tu‘ on your favourite streaming platform - https://umgindia.lnk.to/THT

Featuring - Jitendra Kumar, Zahrah S Khan

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:
Get ready for a high-octane experience with the action-packed teaser of  #Matka! Featuring Varun Tej, Meenakshi Chowdary, and Nora Fatehi, with a powerful soundtrack by GV Prakash Kumar, directed by Karuna Kumar. A thrilling treat awaits!

Stay updated with the latest videos, Subscribe on the link - http://bit.ly/adityamusic
Click here to share on Facebook- https://bit.ly/3v3iHeg  

#MATKA is an upcoming Periodical Film starring Mega Prince Varun tej in the Lead Role, Written and Directed by Karuna Kumar. It also co stars Meenakshi Chowdary, Nora Fatehi, Naveen Chandra and others. Music by GV Prakash Kumar, Cinematography by A Kishor Kumar and Proudly Produced on a massive scale by Dr. Vijender Reddy Teegala and Rajani Talluri under Vyra Entertainments in Association with SRT Entertainments

The story which takes place between 1958-1982 is based on a real incident that shook the entire nation and the story is set in the backdrop of Vizag. The story spans 24 years. 

Cast: #VarunTej, #MeenakshiChowdary, #NoraFatehi, Naveen Chandra, Kannada Kishore, Ajay Ghosh, Mime Gopi, Roopalakshmi, Vijayrama Raju, Jagadeesh, Raj Thirandas.

en-IN.title: Matka Teaser | Varun Tej | Karuna Kumar | Meenakshi Chowdary | Nora Fatehi | GV Prakash Kumar
en-IN.description:
Get ready for a high-octane experience with the action-packed teaser of  #Matka! Featuring Varun Tej, Meenakshi Chowdary, and Nora Fatehi, with a powerful soundtrack by GV Prakash Kumar, directed by Karuna Kumar. A thrilling treat awaits!

Stay updated with the latest videos, Subscribe on the link - http://bit.ly/adityamusic
Click here to share on Facebook- https://bit.ly/3v3iHeg  

#MATKA is an upcoming Periodical Film starring Mega Prince Varun tej in the Lead Role, Written and Directed by Karuna Kumar. It also co stars Meenakshi Chowdary, Nora Fatehi, Naveen Chandra and others. Music by GV Prakash Kumar, Cinematography by A Kishor Kumar and Proudly Produced on a massive scale by Dr. Vijender Reddy Teegala and Rajani Talluri under Vyra Entertainments in Association with SRT Entertainments

The story which takes place between 1958-1982 is based on a real incident that shook the entire nation and the story is set in the backdrop of Vizag. The story spans 24 years. 

Cast: #VarunTej, #MeenakshiChowdary, #NoraFatehi, Naveen Chandra, Kannada Kishore, Ajay Ghosh, Mime Gopi, Roopalakshmi, Vijayrama Raju, Jagadeesh, Raj Thirandas.
